'''「告頂新　討公道」運動'''是指2014年11月17日，[[民進黨|民進黨]][[新北市長|新北市長]]候選人[[游錫堃|游錫堃]]在前[[行政院|行政院]]長[[謝長廷|謝長廷]]、民進黨[[新北市議會|新北市議會]][[黨團|黨團]]成員、游錫堃競選總部幹部陪同下召開[[記者會|記者會]]宣布的一項由[[新北市政府|新北市政府]]向[[頂新|頂新]][[代位求償|代位求償]]為市民爭取公道，每人最多可拿到[[新台幣|新台幣]]500至300,000元賠償金的活動。<ref name="#1">{{cite news | language = zh-tw | url = http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/politics/20141117/507802/%E3%80%90%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8%E3%80%91%E6%B1%82%E5%84%9F%E7%89%8C%EF%BC%81%E6%B8%B8%E9%8C%AB%E5%A0%83%E6%93%AC%E4%BB%A3%E4%BD%8D%E6%B1%82%E5%84%9F%E5%91%8A%E9%A0%82%E6%96%B0 | title = 【大選】求償牌！游錫堃擬代位求償告頂新 | publisher = [[蘋果日報|蘋果日報]] | date = 2014-11-17 | accessdate = 2014-11-24 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304201108/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/politics/20141117/507802/%E3%80%90%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8%E3%80%91%E6%B1%82%E5%84%9F%E7%89%8C%EF%BC%81%E6%B8%B8%E9%8C%AB%E5%A0%83%E6%93%AC%E4%BB%A3%E4%BD%8D%E6%B1%82%E5%84%9F%E5%91%8A%E9%A0%82%E6%96%B0 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language = zh-tw | url =  | title = 游錫堃發起告頂新 連署代位求償 | publisher = [[聯合報|聯合報]] | date =2014-11-17 | accessdate =2014-11-24}}</ref><ref name="#2">{{cite news | language = zh-tw | url = http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/1159154 | title = 游錫堃發起「告頂新，討公道」將代位求償 | publisher = [[自由時報|自由時報]] | date = 2014-11-17 | accessdate = 2014-11-24 | archive-date = 2021-08-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210820071105/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/1159154 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 背景 ==
[[File:委託書2.png|200px]]
[[2014年台灣餿水油事件|台灣油品安全連環爆]]，2014年10月8日，[[頂新集團|頂新集團]]下的[[正義食品|正義食品]]公司「維力清香油」、「維力香豬油」、「正義香豬油」3款[[豬油|豬油]]捲入[[飼料油|飼料油]]風波，讓食安問題再度浮上檯面。<ref>{{cite news | language = zh-tw | url = http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20141008003389-260402 | title = 飼料油混食油 正義油品中招 | publisher = [[中國時報|中國時報]] | date = 2014-10-08 | accessdate = 2014-11-24 | archive-date = 2021-08-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210820065503/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20141008003389-260402 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | language = zh-tw | url = http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201410085001-1.aspx | title = 正義油再陷風暴 頂新：釐清產品 | publisher = [[中央社|中央社]] | date = 2014-10-08 | accessdate = 2014-11-24 | archive-date = 2014-10-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141009092244/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201410085001-1.aspx | dead-url = no }}</ref>2014年10月9日，[[新北市|新北市]]市長[[朱立倫|朱立倫]]表示：「每次食安的事件都讓民眾很不安，我一定要重刑、重罰，罰到這些黑心的廠商，罰到他倒、關到他老，讓他們絕對不敢再犯這樣的錯。」<ref name="#3">{{cite news | language = zh-tw | url = http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/1126660 | title = 正義油品出包 朱立倫：罰到倒、關到老 | publisher = [[自由時報|自由時報]] | date = 2014-10-09 | accessdate = 2014-11-24 | archive-date = 2021-08-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210820065459/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/1126660 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="#4">{{cite news | language = zh-tw | url = http://www.cna.com.tw/news/ahel/201410090144-1.aspx | title = 朱立倫：黑心業者罰到倒關到老 | publisher = [[中央社|中央社]] | date = 2014-10-09 | accessdate = 2014-11-24 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304114643/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/ahel/201410090144-1.aspx | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="#5">{{cite news | language = zh-tw | url = http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20141009/484585/ | title = 黑心油品再起　朱立倫轟：罰到倒關到老 | publisher = [[蘋果日報|蘋果日報]] | date = 2014-10-09 | accessdate = 2014-11-24 | archive-date = 2016-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305014204/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20141009/484585/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

2014年11月17日，[[民進黨|民進黨]][[新北市|新北市]]長候選人[[游錫堃|游錫堃]]表示，政府對[[頂新|頂新]]的消極作為，是讓食安問題連環爆的最大黑手，尤其[[朱立倫|朱立倫]]常說要將黑心廠商「罰到倒、關到老」<ref name="#3"/><ref name="#4"/><ref name="#5"/>，卻在上任後30天就快速通過[[頂新|頂新]]位於[[三重區|三重]]新燕的萬坪土地，希望[[中華民國內政部|內政部]]能將此案退回[[新北市|新北市]]府，重啟調查、釐清變更過程疑點。並發起當選第一天就會成立律師團，並請來[[謝長廷|謝長廷]]擔任首席法律顧問，由[[新北市|新北市]]政府向頂新代位求償，為市民爭取公道的「告頂新　討公道」運動。<ref name="#1"/><ref name="#6">{{cite news | language = zh-tw | url = http://udn.com/NEWS/BREAKINGNEWS/BREAKINGNEWS1/9071059.shtml | title = 游錫堃發起告頂新 連署代位求償 | publisher = [[聯合報|聯合報]] | date = 2014-11-17 | accessdate = 2014-11-24 | archive-date = 2014-11-24 | archive-url = https://archive.is/20141124112156/http://udn.com/NEWS/BREAKINGNEWS/BREAKINGNEWS1/9071059.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="#2"/>

== 活動進程 ==
*2014年11月17日，[[民進黨|民進黨]][[新北市|新北市]]長候選人[[游錫堃|游錫堃]]發起「告頂新　討公道」運動。<ref name="#1"/><ref name="#6"/><ref name="#2"/>
*11月23日，已收到近8000份委託書，並有150多家擁有共同意志的商店參加「告頂新，討公道」的連署。<ref>{{cite news | language = zh-tw | url = http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20141123001820-260407 | title = 百家商店連署告頂新 游錫堃：組律師團 | publisher = [[中國時報|中國時報]] | date = 2014-11-23 | accessdate = 2014-11-24 | archive-date = 2021-08-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210820071119/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20141123001820-260407 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | language = zh-tw | url = http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aipl/201411230129-1.aspx | title = 游：告頂新　已收8千份委託書 | publisher = [[中央社|中央社]] | date = 2014-11-23 | accessdate = 2014-11-24 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304103314/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aipl/201411230129-1.aspx | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | language = zh-tw | url = http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/1164661 | title = 擴大向頂新代位求償 游錫堃邀商家連署 | publisher = [[自由時報|自由時報]] | date = 2014-11-23 | accessdate = 2014-11-24 | archive-date = 2019-05-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190513032141/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/1164661 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

*2015年12月20日，民眾發起「全民監督，解放味全」活動<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.flyingv.cc/project/9632 |title=flyingV全民集資收購味全 |accessdate=2015-12-21 |archive-date=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222120305/https://www.flyingv.cc/project/9632 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，希望於全台灣各大城市舉辦說明會，邀請全台灣的民眾一起參與，募集全台灣之專業、資金、股權、委託書將味全還給社會。

